c: 3
v: 103
t: "Nimufatane k’umugozi w’Imana mwese uko\tmuri kandi ntimusanzarane, kandi mwibuke\timigisha y’Imana iri hejuru yanyu, mugihe mwari abansi kubandi nayo ica irahuza imitima yanyu kumigisha yayo nukuba mwese\tabavandimwe, kandi\tmwari\tkunkengera\ty’ikinogo\tc’umuriro\twa Jahannamu\tnayo\tica\tirabarokora\tnuwo\tmuriro, uko\trero\tniko\tImana ibabenyesha amajambo yayo matagatifu kugira ngo mushobore kurongoka"